參考[編輯]


^ Peskin, M.E., Schroeder, D.V. (1995). An Introduction to Quantum Field Theory, Westview Press, ISBN 0-201-50397-2, p. 80.
^ Mandl, F., Shaw, G. (1984/2002). Quantum Field Theory, John Wiley & Sons, Chichester UK, revised edition, ISBN 0-471-94186-7, pp. 56, 176.
^ Bayfield, J. E.(1999). Quantum Evolution: an Introduction to Time-Dependent Quantum Mechanics, John Wiley, New York, ISBN 0-471-18174-9, p. 62.
^ Larry Gilman"Virtual Particles"
^ David Raymond(2006)"Virtual Particles"


外部連結[編輯]

Are virtual particles really constantly popping in and out of existence? — Gordon Kane, director of the Michigan Center for Theoretical Physics at the University of Michigan at Ann Arbor, proposes an answer at the Scientific American website.
Virtual Particles: What are they?





 
